; Coverage test for xact.cc
; auto_xact expression that returns non-amount throws error

= Expenses
    (Budget:Match)    (payee)

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 9:
While applying automated transaction from "$FILE", lines 4-5:
> = Expenses
>     (Budget:Match)    (payee)
While extending transaction from "$FILE", lines 7-9:
> 2024/01/01 Test
>     Expenses:Food    $10.00
>     Assets:Cash
Error: Amount expressions must result in a simple amount
end test
